aver' |publisher=Deadline.com |date=2014-03-05 |accessdate=2014-05-12}}</ref>3月7日，宣布《[[絕望的主婦|慾望師奶]]》[[費利西蒂·赫夫曼|費莉希蒂·霍夫曼]]將與赫頓共同擔任主角，並飾演羅斯（赫頓飾演）的前妻兼被害者母親芭兒·斯寇奇。<ref>{{cite web|last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/03/felicity-huffman-american-crime-john-ridley-abc/ |title=Felicity Huffman To Star In John Ridley's ABC Pilot 'American Crime' |publisher=Deadline.com |date=2014-03-07 |accessdate=2014-05-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Goldberg|first=Lesley |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/felicity-huffman-star-abc-drama-686812 |title=Felicity Huffman to Star in ABC Drama From '12 Years a Slave' Writer |work=好萊塢報導|date=2014-03-07 |accessdate=2014-05-12}}</ref>

